AUTHERENS PART 1: THE LOST PARADISE
A complete epic fantasy experience, available exclusively as a one-time Patreon purchase for USD40. No subscription required.
What happens when death is not the end—but the beginning of an entirely new universe?
Autherens Part 1: The Lost Paradise begins with Armenis, an exiled seeker of forbidden knowledge, dying upon a ruined Earth. Beyond death, he awakens as Garodha, celestial scribe of Paradisio and keeper of the mysterious Book of Earth.
But Paradise is not peaceful.
An ambitious Empress desires the forbidden book. A fallen lover returns as the warlock Warloxus. Guardian Lord Quixham moves between heaven and hell with uncertain loyalties. Love, jealousy, prophecy and material desire begin to fracture the celestial order.
When Emperor Autheraeneus becomes the first being to die in Paradise, his final act gives birth to a new universe:
The Autherens.
From that death emerge competing powers—the red robe of eternal love and the purple robe of material domination. Garodha, Heraldian and Amelus must cross broken heavens, supernatural kingdoms, dynastic conflicts and realms shaped by consciousness itself as the struggle for the new universe begins.
This is not a conventional fantasy tale.
It is a vast metaphysical epic exploring:
- death, rebirth and the afterlife;
- forbidden knowledge and the power of authorship;
- damaged families and inherited suffering;
- love as both salvation and sacrifice;
- heaven, hell and realities created through consciousness;
- royal dynasties, prophecies and competing spiritual powers;
- the creation of an entirely original fantasy universe.
The story expands across Paradisio, Mortal Paradisio, Jarasha, Ferisha, Garantula and the newly forming Autherential universe. Its ten chapters contain wars, weddings, betrayals, curses, supernatural transformations, rival robes of power and generations shaped by the choices of those who came before them.
At the centre of the story is Garodha: historian, creator, father, celestial servant and deeply imperfect guardian. He must confront a terrible question:
Can a creator guide the lives of those he loves without eventually trying to control them?
Your purchase includes
- permanent access to the complete Autherens Part 1 Patreon post;
- ten extensive chapters and a concluding epilogue;
- the beginning of the wider Autherens mythology;
- an original world of celestial courts, supernatural bloodlines, metaphysical realms and competing dynasties;
- direct support for an independent author building a fantasy universe outside the conventional publishing system.
The story begins with the death and rebirth of Armenis, who crosses from a burning Earth into a realm of beauty, consciousness and divine creation—only to discover that even Paradise can be corrupted by entitlement, fear and the desire to possess forbidden knowledge.
Later, the death of Emperor Autheraeneus becomes the foundation of the universe that bears his name, while the forces of love and material domination divide the future into two rival sovereignties.
Price: USD40 — one-time purchase.
No monthly membership is required.
Enter Paradisio. Witness its fall. Discover the birth of the Autherens.
Purchase now and begin the journey into The Lost Paradise.
